      "text": [
        "348 - وَ سُئِلَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنْ تَوْجِيهِ اَلْمَيِّتِ فَقَالَ «اِسْتَقْبِلْ بِبَاطِنِ قَدَمَيْهِ اَلْقِبْلَةَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.348 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about the positioning of the deceased, and Imam (as) said: \"Direct the soles of their feet toward the Qibla”."
        ]
      }
    }
